mame-system-media — licensing and preservation notice
=======================================================

This repository contains two kinds of material with different rights. Please
read both sections before reusing anything.


1. Original work by Dave Rand
-----------------------------

The documentation (all README files), the CP/M CBIOS I authored, the bootable
disk images I formatted and curated, my own disk-recovery images, and the
photographs of my own hardware are:

